Welcome

Welcome to my co-op portfolio! Here you'll find my experiences, skills, and reflections from my work terms. Explore the projects, roles, and growth throughout my journey!

{/* Work Term 1 Section */}

Work Term 1: SAP CI/CD Pipeline Developer

My first SAP work term focused on CI/CD pipeline automation, collaboration, and technical growth. I worked with a team to improve deployment processes, documentation, and cross-functional communication.

Key Highlights

  • Built automated CI/CD pipelines for efficient deployment cycles
  • Collaborated with developers and QA to enhance workflow
  • Documented new processes and trained team members

Skills Developed

  • Teamwork & Agile Collaboration
  • Problem-solving with technical tools
  • Continuous Integration & Deployment
